    "body": "Introduced in #8611.\r\n\r\nChange caused by this PR:\r\n\r\n## [0] NVIDIA B200\r\n\r\n|  T{ct}  |  OffsetT{ct}  |  Elements{io}  |   Ref Time |   Ref Noise |   Cmp Time |   Cmp Noise |        Diff |   %Diff |  Status  |\r\n|---------|---------------|----------------|------------|-------------|------------|-------------|-------------|---------|----------|\r\n|   I8    |      I64      |      2^16      |   9.312 us |       6.27% |  11.180 us |       0.94% |    1.868 us |  20.06% |  🔴 SLOW  |\r\n|   I8    |      I64      |      2^20      |  12.742 us |       7.78% |  13.393 us |       4.28% |    0.651 us |   5.11% |  🔴 SLOW  |\r\n|   I8    |      I64      |      2^24      |  29.897 us |       3.85% |  26.068 us |       2.99% |   -3.829 us | -12.81% |  🟢 FAST  |\r\n|   I8    |      I64      |      2^28      | 228.980 us |       0.49% | 214.950 us |       0.60% |  -14.030 us |  -6.13% |  🟢 FAST  |\r\n|   I8    |      I64      |      2^32      |   3.451 ms |       0.04% |   3.237 ms |       0.24% | -213.883 us |  -6.20% |  🟢 FAST  |\r\n\r\nFixes: #8688 ",
